The Muppets;;80;;95;;PG;;Walter, the world's biggest Muppet fan, is on vacation in Los Angeles with his brother Gary (Jason Segel) and Gary's girlfriend, Mary (Amy Adams). They discover that greedy Tex Richman (Chris Cooper) plans to raze Muppet Studios and drill for oil on the spot. Desperate to save the Muppets' former stomping grounds, the three friends join forces with Kermit to reunite Miss Piggy, Fozzie and the rest of the gang to hold a telethon to raise the $10 million they need to save the studio .;;Kids & family,Comedy;;James Bobin;;2011;;Jason Segel,Amy Adams,Chris Cooper,Rashida Jones,Alan Arkin,James Carville,Donald Glover,Feist,Ken Jeong,Judd Hirsch,Rico Rodriguez,Jack Black,Whoopi Goldberg,Neil Patrick Harris,Selena Gomez,John Krasinski,Mickey Rooney,Zach Galifianakis,Sarah Silverman,Emily Blunt;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_muppets